# Competitor baseline: Caddy as a pure reverse proxy to the SAME upstream.
# Go integrated proxy (the GC/memory comparison). auto_https off so it never tries ACME on the
# plain :8080 listener; admin off trims the control surface. No access log block == logging off,
# matching EdgeGuard's RUST_LOG=warn. reverse_proxy pools upstream connections by default.

{
	admin off
	auto_https off
	persist_config off
}

:8080 {
	reverse_proxy upstream:80
}
